Source: libidn2
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Tux Mason <tuxmason@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: libunistring-dev
Standards-Version: 3.9.5
Homepage: https://www.gnu.org/software/libidn/#libidn2

Package: libidn2
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libc (>= 1.1.8), ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: provides an implementation of the IDNA2008 + TR46 specifications
 Libidn2 is an implementation of the IDNA2008 + TR46 specifications
 (RFC 5890, RFC 5891, RFC 5892, RFC 5893, TR 46).
 .
 This package provides the shared library libidn2.

Package: idn2
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libc (>= 1.1.8), ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: a command line interface to libidn2
 idn2 is a command line interface to the internationalized domain
 library.

Package: libidn2-dev
Section: libdevel
Provides: idn2-dev
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libidn2 (= ${binary:Version}), libunistring-dev
Description: Development headers and libidn2 static library
 This package provides libidn2.a, headers and pkgconfig data required
 to build applications, libraries or plugins using the libidn2 API.

Package: libidn2-doc
Section: doc
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Recommends: man-db
Depends: idn2 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: documentation for idn2
 This package provides info and man pages for libidn2.
